166
00:20:31,651 --> 00:20:35,255
za to draho zaplatia.

167
00:20:44,189 --> 00:20:45,839
Je to všetko kvôli mne.

168
00:21:03,201 --> 00:21:05,059
Ako sa opovažujú takto chovať?

169
00:21:05,059 --> 00:21:07,900
